	<div class="main-content-div col p-0 position-relative">
		<div class="w-100 d-flex align-items-center flex-column px-4 pt-4" id="calculator">
			<div class="w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column px-lg-4 pb-3">
				<div class="w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center position-relative mb-2">
					<div class="w-100 flex-grow-1 border-top border-dark"></div>
					<h1 class="font-header w-100 text-center m-0 px-0">Calculator</h1>
					<div class="w-100 flex-grow-1 border-top border-dark"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="w-100 mb-3">
					<h2 class="font-subheader w-100 font-weight-bold text-underline mb-2" id="calc-how-to">Instructions</h2>
					<div class="font-content w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column mb-4">
						<p class="w-100 text-justify">This calculator will display the possible bonus stats you can get when flaming an item. To begin, enter your equipment's level. Keying in your weapon's base WA/MA is optional. Finally, select your equip's "type" and the flame to be used. The calculator will automatically update the table below based on your input.</p>

						<p class="w-100 text-justify">If you are unsure what category your equipment belongs to, see the About Flames - Item Types section. As a quick reference, Zero weapons and Chaos Root Abyss boss helmets are considered Normal type. Most unique equipment dropped by bosses and Meister Ear Studs are Special type.</p>

						<p class="w-100 text-justify"><strong>Important:</strong> For Zero weapons, key in Lapis' (Beta's weapon) WA.</p>
					</div>
					<h2 class="font-subheader w-100 font-weight-bold text-underline mb-2" id="calc-settings">Settings</h2>
					<div class="font-content d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-4">
						<form class="font-form size-720 w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column flex-lg-row">
							<div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
								<div class="form-group row d-flex align-items-center">
									<label for="gear-level" class="col-4 col-lg-6 col-form-label font-weight-bold text-left pl-0">Equip Level</label>
									<div class="col-8 col-lg-6 d-flex">
										<input class="font-small w-100 form-control text-center rounded-sm" type="number" id="gear-level" value=0>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group row d-flex align-items-center">
									<label for="base-wa-ma" class="col-4 col-lg-6 col-form-label font-weight-bold text-left pl-0">Weapon Base WA/MA</label>
									<div class="col-8 col-lg-6 d-flex">
										<input class="font-small w-100 form-control text-center rounded-sm" type="number" id="base-wa-ma" value=0>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
								<div class="form-group row d-flex align-items-center">
									<label for="equip-level" class="col-4 col-lg-4 col-form-label font-weight-bold text-left pl-0">Equip Type</label>
									<div class="col-8 col-lg-8 radio-select-group d-flex justify-content-center">
										<div class="col form-check p-0">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="equip-type-radio" id="equip-type-normal" value="normal">
											<label class="form-check-label font-small radio-select equip-type-input d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center cursor-pointer px-2" for="equip-type-normal" data-equip-type="normal">Normal</label>
										</div>
										<!--<div class="col form-check p-0">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="equip-type-radio" id="equip-type-eb" value="eb">
											<label class="form-check-label font-small radio-select equip-type-input d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center cursor-pointer px-2" for="equip-type-eb" data-equip-type="eb">Elite Boss</label>
										</div>-->
										<div class="col form-check p-0">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="equip-type-radio" id="equip-type-special" value="boss">
											<label class="form-check-label font-small radio-select equip-type-input d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center cursor-pointer px-2" for="equip-type-special" data-equip-type="boss">Special</label>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group row d-flex align-items-center">
									<label for="equip-level" class="col-4 col-lg-4 col-form-label font-weight-bold text-left pl-0">Flame Type</label>
									<div class="col-8 col-lg-8 radio-select-group d-flex justify-content-center">
										<div class="col form-check p-0">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="flame-type-radio" id="flame-type-crimson" value="crimson">
											<label class="form-check-label font-small radio-select flame-type-input d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center cursor-pointer px-2" for="flame-type-crimson" data-flame-type="crimson" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Crimson / Obsidian Resurrection Flame">
												<img src="./public/images/flames/flame-crimson.png" class="small-img">
												<img src="./public/images/flames/flame-obsidian.png" class="small-img">
											</label>
										</div>
										<div class="col form-check p-0">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="flame-type-radio" id="flame-type-rainbow" value="rainbow">
											<label class="form-check-label font-small radio-select flame-type-input d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center cursor-pointer px-2" for="flame-type-rainbow" data-flame-type="rainbow" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Rainbow / Black Resurrection Flame">
												<img src="./public/images/flames/flame-rainbow.png" class="small-img">
												<img src="./public/images/flames/flame-black.png" class="small-img">
											</label>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</form>
